I didn't expect them to be together so soon.

17
00:01:03,330 --> 00:01:05,310
Lin Ke looks elegant.

18
00:01:05,510 --> 00:01:07,600
So it surprises me that he acted so quickly.

19
00:01:07,600 --> 00:01:09,060
He did better than Ji.

20
00:01:09,350 --> 00:01:11,050
Why are these two here

21
00:01:11,080 --> 00:01:12,660
