22
00:01:15,360 --> 00:01:16,240
Ji.

23
00:01:17,730 --> 00:01:19,820
Are you leaving now?

24
00:01:20,180 --> 00:01:21,280
No, not yet.

25
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:22,950
The car I booked will arrive later.

26
00:01:22,950 --> 00:01:24,210
I'll wait here.

27
00:01:28,010 --> 00:01:30,680
Is he going to watch our daughter leaving for her blind date?

28
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:32,970
He is such an awkward young man.

29
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:41,820
Why don't you make yourself look nice for the blind date?

30
00:01:41,910 --> 00:01:44,310
What would Dr. Li think of your appearance?

31
00:01:44,479 --> 00:01:46,350
You're really pissing me off.

32
00:01:47,110 --> 00:01:48,310
I'll go get changed now.

33
00:01:48,310 --> 00:01:49,289
Forget it.

34
00:01:49,520 --> 00:01:51,870
It's almost noon. Go to the restaurant now.

35
00:01:51,870 --> 00:01:53,930
Don't be late and keep Dr. Li waiting.

36
00:02:09,669 --> 00:02:12,550
Why aren't young people these days as direct anymore?

37
00:02:12,550 --> 00:02:15,330
His girl is about to date someone else,
but he still hasn't told her how he feels.

38
00:02:15,330 --> 00:02:16,890
What is he waiting for?

39
00:02:16,910 --> 00:02:18,220
Calm down.

40
00:02:19,470 --> 00:02:20,440
Honey,

41
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:23,650
what's the name of the restaurant

42
00:02:23,710 --> 00:02:25,310
you booked for our daughter's blind date?

43
00:02:25,310 --> 00:02:26,670
I'd like to know the details.

44
00:02:26,670 --> 00:02:28,410
Don't worry.

45
00:02:28,490 --> 00:02:32,829
I booked the most famous one on the internet, Little Paris.

46
00:02:33,079 --> 00:02:37,950
I heard that all blind dates there went successful.

47
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:40,150
Little Paris?

48
00:02:40,310 --> 00:02:42,310
Is that the one near Xikou?

49
00:02:42,390 --> 00:02:42,990
Yes.

50
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:43,800
It's not very far.

51
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:45,680
You can even get there by running.

52
00:02:58,820 --> 00:03:01,920
Finally, here's the silver lining.

53
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,910
I've been so worried for the past few days.

54
00:03:03,910 --> 00:03:05,300
I'm so anxious about them.

55
00:03:05,300 --> 00:03:07,880
Finally, he is doing the right thing.

56
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:09,440
Let's go and find out what's happening.

57
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:09,860
Let's go.

58
00:03:09,860 --> 00:03:10,540
Let's go.

59
00:03:28,190 --> 00:03:29,200
This is good.

60
00:03:29,200 --> 00:03:30,550
These will make great materials

61
00:03:30,550 --> 00:03:32,390
for their future wedding.

62
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,600
Let's go. Now.

63
00:03:33,600 --> 00:03:34,150
Let's go.

64
00:03:34,310 --> 00:03:37,370
Miss Qiu, your work is in the computer industry, right?

65
00:03:38,310 --> 00:03:38,990
Yes.

66
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:41,110
I'm a game designer.

67
00:03:42,310 --> 00:03:42,950
I see.

68
00:03:43,230 --> 00:03:44,430
It's a stressful job,

69
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:45,230
but

70
00:03:45,310 --> 00:03:47,220
it would be better if you adjusted your schedule
and worked out more.

71
00:03:47,220 --> 00:03:49,950
After all, health is the foundation of good work.

72
00:03:50,310 --> 00:03:51,260
Thank you, Dr. Li.

73
00:03:51,260 --> 00:03:52,520
I’ll keep that in mind.

74
00:03:52,829 --> 00:03:54,990
After all, I'm not that young anymore.

75
00:03:55,920 --> 00:03:56,870
Nonsense.

76
00:03:56,990 --> 00:03:58,070
You're so lovely

77
00:03:58,170 --> 00:03:58,990
and nice.

78
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:02,850
It's the first time anyone has called me lovely.

79
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:05,630
Dr. Li, you're too kind.

80
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:07,360
I'm not being kind.

81
00:04:07,510 --> 00:04:08,870
I'm telling the truth.

82
00:04:09,470 --> 00:04:11,330
Aunt Fang is a nice person as well.

83
00:04:11,350 --> 00:04:13,070
She's kind and generous.

84
00:04:14,220 --> 00:04:15,020
That's right.

85
00:04:15,130 --> 00:04:16,920
I think my mom is great too.

86
00:04:17,370 --> 00:04:19,149
We are well-suited for each other.

87
00:04:19,149 --> 00:04:21,050
Actually, I really like your parents

88
00:04:21,050 --> 00:04:22,290
and the environment of your family.

89
00:04:22,290 --> 00:04:23,950
It makes me like you even more.

90
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:26,010
We'll be perfect together.

91
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:28,250
Oh, okay.

92
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:30,800
Look. This meal

93
00:04:31,030 --> 00:04:32,560
