98
00:04:41,870 --> 00:04:43,290
Plum duck: 600 calories.

99
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:45,280
Sweet and sour pork ribs: 490 calories.

100
00:04:45,280 --> 00:04:46,590
That's a total

101
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:49,020
of 1,570 calories.

102
00:04:52,840 --> 00:04:53,550
Miss Qiu.

103
00:04:55,700 --> 00:04:58,300
♫Waking up as if nothing happened♫

104
00:04:56,510 --> 00:04:57,510
Miss Qiu.

105
00:04:59,610 --> 00:05:02,220
♫A cup of coffee to keep me going♫

106
00:05:00,880 --> 00:05:02,400
Are you feeling ill,

107
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:04,390
or do you not like the food?

108
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:05,630
♫Some memories♫

109
00:05:05,990 --> 00:05:10,460
♫Are like nightmares♫

110
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,810
It's just what you said

111
00:05:08,910 --> 00:05:10,650
reminded me of someone.

112
00:05:11,170 --> 00:05:12,410
May I ask

113
00:05:12,310 --> 00:05:15,360
♫A bit calm♫

114
00:05:12,470 --> 00:05:14,730
who is the person you're thinking of now?

115
00:05:15,910 --> 00:05:19,140
♫Yet a bit restless♫

116
00:05:17,950 --> 00:05:18,880
That would be me.

117
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:22,940
♫Turns out I was just being♫

118
00:05:23,570 --> 00:05:26,050
♫Too sentimental♫

119
00:05:28,510 --> 00:05:31,800
♫I turned away to prove♫

120
00:05:29,200 --> 00:05:30,280
Ji Xuan.

121
00:05:32,770 --> 00:05:36,020
♫I never cared♫

122
00:05:34,990 --> 00:05:36,159
I'm sorry, Dr. Li.

123
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:38,680
I know this might be rude,

124
00:05:36,940 --> 00:05:40,520
♫My caring, my indifference♫

125
00:05:39,150 --> 00:05:40,230
but I don't think

126
00:05:40,380 --> 00:05:42,940
Feifei needs this blind date anymore.

127
00:05:41,150 --> 00:05:44,450
♫They were all just a game♫

128
00:05:45,190 --> 00:05:52,170
♫Good morning, Good night♫

129
00:05:45,950 --> 00:05:46,680
That's fine.

130
00:05:52,780 --> 00:06:00,020
♫I love myself more than you do♫

131
00:05:56,570 --> 00:06:04,490
[CinemaScope]

132
00:05:57,690 --> 00:05:58,860
Why did you come here?

133
00:05:58,860 --> 00:06:00,060
I was just passing by.

134
00:06:00,150 --> 00:06:01,710
and saw someone who looked miserable,

135
00:06:00,850 --> 00:06:04,580
♫I will never mention that♫

136
00:06:01,710 --> 00:06:03,280
so I wanted to help her out.

137
00:06:03,630 --> 00:06:04,800
Ji Xuan.

138
00:06:04,990 --> 00:06:06,270
I'm joking with you.

139
00:06:09,210 --> 00:06:11,050
Who told you I'm at Little Paris?

140
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:12,120
It's a secret.

141
00:06:14,350 --> 00:06:15,260
Well,

142
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:18,800
why did you come here?

143
00:06:18,870 --> 00:06:20,470
I can't tell you now.

144
00:06:21,070 --> 00:06:23,130
But I promise I'll tell you very soon.

145
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:24,770
Could you wait for me

146
00:06:25,430 --> 00:06:26,640
until then?

147
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:28,840
[CinemaScope]

148
00:06:30,310 --> 00:06:31,590
You go home first.

149
00:06:31,650 --> 00:06:33,020
I'll go see you later.

150
00:06:34,510 --> 00:06:35,150
Well...

151
00:06:35,630 --> 00:06:43,280
[CinemaScope]

152
00:06:37,270 --> 00:06:37,990
Okay.

153
00:06:44,350 --> 00:06:44,950
Bye.

154
00:06:50,210 --> 00:06:54,260
[CinemaScope]

155
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:57,840
Dad.

156
00:06:58,310 --> 00:06:58,760
Mom.

157
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:03,640
We don't have a grown-up son like you.

158
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,520
Earlier at Little Paris,

159
00:07:07,950 --> 00:07:10,480
Dr. Li said something that touched me deeply.

160
00:07:10,880 --> 00:07:11,550
He said

161
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:14,030
he likes Feifei's family,

162
00:07:14,270 --> 00:07:16,800
which makes him wants to be with her even more.

163
00:07:17,330 --> 00:07:18,680
I'm really an orphan.

164
00:07:19,270 --> 00:07:20,590
Since I was young,

165
00:07:21,830 --> 00:07:23,740
I've never felt a parent's love.

166
00:07:25,870 --> 00:07:28,000
But ever since I came to the Qiu family,

167
00:07:28,710 --> 00:07:29,590
Feifei,

168
00:07:30,460 --> 00:07:31,030
you,

169
00:07:31,870 --> 00:07:32,770
and dad

170
00:07:33,440 --> 00:07:35,830
have made me feel the warmth of a family.

171
00:07:37,610 --> 00:07:39,610
The beginning between Feifei and me

172
00:07:39,830 --> 00:07:41,450
might not have been simple and pure,

173
00:07:41,450 --> 00:07:44,320
but what I feel for her is very real.

174
00:07:47,659 --> 00:07:49,090
I not only like Feifei,

175
00:07:50,310 --> 00:07:52,590
but I also like the Qiu family.

176
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:56,830
I hope to be with her

177
00:07:57,159 --> 00:07:59,570
and become a member of the Qiu family.

178
00:08:01,100 --> 00:08:01,680
Dad.

179
00:08:02,350 --> 00:08:02,830
Mom.

180
00:08:03,760 --> 00:08:05,110
Please give me a chance

181
00:08:05,860 --> 00:08:08,320
to pursue Feifei seriously, just this once.

182
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:11,600
That was a great speech.

183
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:13,780
But your life experience…

184
00:08:14,190 --> 00:08:15,320
It is a little

185
00:08:15,590 --> 00:08:16,790
hard for us to accept.

186
00:08:17,950 --> 00:08:18,680
Also,

187
00:08:19,590 --> 00:08:21,450
this rental boyfriend business…

188
00:08:21,700 --> 00:08:23,900
Doesn't that just make you a con artist?

189
00:08:24,810 --> 00:08:26,080
Among many other things,

190
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:27,210
you're still seeing

191
00:08:27,230 --> 00:08:29,460
other young women.

192
00:08:29,990 --> 00:08:30,820
You're right.

193
00:08:31,630 --> 00:08:32,510
Therefore,

194
00:08:32,860 --> 00:08:34,840
when I decided to pursue Feifei,

195
00:08:34,950 --> 00:08:36,120
I made up my mind

196
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:40,380
that I wouldn’t engage in anything
like being a rental boyfriend ever again.

197
00:08:40,470 --> 00:08:42,809
[WeChat]

198
00:08:48,530 --> 00:08:49,220
Dad.

199
00:08:50,030 --> 00:08:50,710
Mom.

200
00:08:51,940 --> 00:08:54,180
I will never upset Feifei.

201
00:08:55,390 --> 00:08:58,000
Please give me a chance.

202
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:08,660
Feifei.

203
00:09:10,070 --> 00:09:11,210
Ji Xuan.

204
00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:15,880
Ji Xuan.

205
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:16,970
You...

206
00:09:17,150 --> 00:09:18,190
You're back.

207
00:09:18,190 --> 00:09:19,200
I'm back.

208
00:09:19,460 --> 00:09:20,130
Feifei,

209
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:22,810
would you take this once-in-a-lifetime opportunity?

210
00:09:22,810 --> 00:09:23,840
No need to spend money

211
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:24,900
or build up affection.

212
00:09:24,900 --> 00:09:27,470
You could have a sunny, filial boyfriend.

213
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:28,600
Would you

214
00:09:29,150 --> 00:09:30,110
like that?

215
00:09:30,390 --> 00:09:31,910
Are you kidding me?

216
00:09:31,910 --> 00:09:33,630
I'm not kidding. I'm serious.

217
00:09:34,110 --> 00:09:35,260
I just want

218
00:09:35,580 --> 00:09:36,630
a kiss from you.

219
00:09:38,260 --> 00:09:40,170
Do you want me to be your boyfriend or not?

220
00:09:40,170 --> 00:09:41,380
No, I don't.

221
00:09:40,870 --> 00:09:42,980
♫Today is Monday, and the cycle begins again♫

222
00:09:43,470 --> 00:09:45,500
♫Everything I do seems purposeless♫

223
00:09:43,510 --> 00:09:45,950
I'm sure it's a value-added service.

224
00:09:45,990 --> 00:09:49,500
♫Should I run away or wait for things to turn around?♫

225
00:09:46,030 --> 00:09:47,510
I won't be fooled again.

226
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:51,390
I don't need to pay me money.

227
00:09:51,390 --> 00:09:53,560
♫Decide now, no more doubts♫

228
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:53,050
Because from now on,

229
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:55,590
I'm officially your boyfriend.

230
00:09:54,070 --> 00:09:56,350
♫All the most important decisions♫

231
00:09:56,310 --> 00:09:58,030
I will only serve you, Qiu Feifei.

232
00:09:56,770 --> 00:09:58,830
♫Change the environment; love yourself first♫

233
00:09:58,480 --> 00:10:00,350
All of your requests will be free of charge.

234
00:09:59,390 --> 00:10:01,330
♫There will be surprises♫

235
00:10:02,650 --> 00:10:06,970
♫Being strong or fragile; I will never lie♫

236
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:10,890
♫There's no need to act tough for anyone♫

237
00:10:13,100 --> 00:10:17,570
♫Plain or madness; just a thought apart♫

238
00:10:18,250 --> 00:10:21,250
♫When I wake up; I welcome a new imagination♫
